      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3AE1AAEB-99ED-48AC-A942-4BD9406CE222" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate and select the file you want to link to the assignment [1]. Click the <strong>Add </strong>button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
